-- Value Partners Plans to Raise Up to HK$795.2 Million to Expand into China
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-14T22:18:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/value-partners-to-raise-up-to-hk-795-2-million-in-share-placing-to-expand.html
Value Partners Group Ltd . will raise
as much as HK$795.2 million to expand into China and as seed
capital for new funds through a placing of as many as 140
million shares at HK$5.68 each, the company said in a Hong Kong
stock exchange filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
